<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-17 14:34 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9868 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e BC-VIDEO-COLUMN-LADN &LR;      02-17 0695
