<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-17 14:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9895 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u e BC-MUSIC-JUDDS-HNS &LR;      02-17 1140
