Scientists at the University of Manchester say this is due to a
pleasure-inducing hearing mechanism we've inherited from fish. 480
words. By Rachel Nowak. Slugged:
BC-LOUD-PLEASURES-(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF)
</P>
