   INDIA'S TESTS POLLUTE PAKISTAN &LR;  _ Plutonium from nuclear bombs
exploded underground by India has polluted Pakistan's nuclear test
site 800 kilometers away, according to U.S. intelligence agents.
180 words. By Rachel Nowak. (Slugged:
BC-INDIA'S-BOMBS-POLLUTE-PAKISTAN-(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF)
