<HEADER>
A9984 &Cx1f; ttf-z
u f BC-GRAPHICS-EARLY-BUDGET     02-17 0413
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHICS-EARLY-BUDGET-NYT </SLUG>
  
