<HEADLINE>
WE ASKED FOR 'EM, WE GOT 'EM: THOSE READER IDEAS CAME ROLLING IN
</HEADLINE>
 (Resending to fix coding) 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By KATHY HARRIS 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The readers have spoken, and they feel strongly about the design
of the Texas quarter, to be introduced in 2004. In a previous
article, we offered some wacky ideas about the upcoming Texas
