<P>
   OLYMPICS
</P>
<P>
   GOODWILL-DOWNHILL _ LAKE PLACID, N.Y. _ Coverage of the first of
two men's downhill events at the winter Goodwill Games. (Rosen,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 18.
</P>
<P>
