<P>
   A Boston Globe article incorrectly reported that Bell Atlantic
Corp. has already acquired nearly 1 million long-distance customers
in New York. Bell Atlantic says it is signing up customers for its
new long-distance service in New York State at a rate that will
meet its goal of having 1 million such customers by year's end.
</P>
