<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-17 20:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0218 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-FRIEDMAN-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      02-17 0785
